Ungoladan invaders in Óinsbridge have been defeated.

Óinsbridge stands where the Forest River snakes into Mirkwood at the edge of the Thornholt,. A once-mighty span that has crumbled to a precipitous and treacherous skeleton athwart the water, now under siege by the regrouping Ungoledain.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Óinsbridge: Scurrying Spiders to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
